apertium-tg-fa
Apertium Tajik to Persian data

--

To compile this dictionary you need to check out lttoolbox-unicode
from the Apertium SVN repository

svn co https://apertium.svn.sourceforge.net/svnroot/apertium/lttoolbox-unicode

Install it into a local directory, for example /home/<username>/local -- 
so that it doesn't interfere with any other lttoolbox installation you have.

Then edit the Makefile and set LTPROC= to the path to your lt-comp binary.

You also need to check out apertium-unicode

svn co https://apertium.svn.sourceforge.net/svnroot/apertium/apertium-unicode

Do the same with this.
